  what is Maven?

   --> java build-tool
   --> dependency management-tool
   --> document generation tool
       
        --> bug reports
        --> code-style reports
        --> unit-testing reports

------------------------------------

how to install Maven ?


1. command-line use       

   --> download maven from apache-site and configure

2. to use in IDE

   --> all latest IDE , already have maven installed.     

